1 0 0 1 66.0 661.0 Tm (- Acknowledge the price concern without panic) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 647.0 Tm (- Find out what "too expensive" actually means) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 633.0 Tm (- Reconnect cost to value the prospect named) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 619.0 Tm (- Hold your price honestly, or say you cannot help) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 599.0 Tm (What "too expensive" can mean) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 582.0 Tm (- Compared to a competitor or their current tool.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 568.0 Tm (- More than the budget they have this quarter.) Tj
